1) When we use List Box when we search a text in list box after we have to remove highlight when we closing the list box.
2) When we use List Box when we search a text in list box after we have to remove the searched text when we closing the list box.
3) Whenever we implement Text Area we have to implement Max size(1-2000) below of the text area.\
4) If npm install will fails then we have to use the below commands
      npm cache clean --force
      npm install -g @angular/cli@latest

